author: Huawei
description:
#Huawei and the Kuwait Foundation for the Advancement of Sciences (KFAS) have launched the Pioneers of Tomorrow's Technology program, offering advanced 5G and AI training to 15 outstanding Kuwaiti students.

Through this initiative, Huawei and KFAS reaffirm their shared mission to nurture local talent, promote cross-border knowledge exchange, and drive Kuwait's digital transformation under Vision 2035.

Watch now to learn more about the program and hear from the participating members!
title: Pioneers of Tomorrow's Technology: Empowering Kuwaiti Youth with KFAS
